<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="margin: 0cm; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: normal;"><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ພວກເຮົາໃຊ້ເທັກໂນໂລຍີການຕິດຕາມເຊັ່ນ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">cookies </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ແລະ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">web beacons </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ເພື່ອເກັບກໍາຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບທ່ານ ຄຸກກີ້ແມ່ນໄຟລ໌ຂໍ້ມູນຂະໜາດນ້ອຍທີ່ເກັບໄວ້ໃນຮາດໄດຂອງທ່ານ ຫຼື ຢູ່ໃນຫນ່ວຍຄວາມຈໍາຂອງອຸປະກອນຂອງທ່ານ. ທີ່ຊ່ວຍພວກເຮົາປັບປຸງ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">&ldquo;</span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ຄິດຮອດ</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">&rdquo; </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ແລະ ປະສົບການຂອງທ່ານເຊັ່ນ: ເບິ່ງຄຸນສົມບັດ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">&ldquo;</span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ຄິດຮອດ</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">&rdquo; </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ທີ່ນິຍົມ ແລະ ການນັບການເຂົ້າຊົມເວັບ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">beacons (</span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ຊຶ່ງເອີ້ນກັນວ່າ "ພິກເຊວແທັກ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">pixels" </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ຫຼື "ເຄລຍ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">GIF</span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">") ແມ່ນຮູບພາບອີເລັກໂທຣນິກທີ່ພວກເຮົາໃຊ້ໃນ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">&ldquo;</span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ຄິດຮອດ</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">&rdquo; </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ເພື່ອຊ່ວຍຈັດສົ່ງ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">cookies, </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ນັບການເຂົ້າຊົມ ແລະ ເຂົ້າໃຈການນໍາໃຊ້ງານ. ພວກເຮົາຍັງເຮັດວຽກຮ່ວມກັບຜູ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິການການວິເຄາະທີ່ເປັນບຸກຄົນທີສາມທີ່ໃຊ້ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">cookies, web beacons, </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ຕົວລະບຸອຸປະກອນ ແລະ ​ເຕັກ​ໂນ​ໂລ​ຊີ​ອື່ນໆ​ ເພື່ອເກັບກໍາຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບການນໍາໃຊ້ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">&ldquo;</span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ຄິດຮອດ</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">&rdquo; </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ຂອງທ່ານ</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">, </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ລວມທັງທີ່ຢູ່ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">IP </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ຂອງທ່ານ</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">, </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ຕົວທ່ອງເວັບ(</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">Web Browser</span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">) ຂໍ້​ມູນ​ເຄືອ​ຂ່າຍ​ໂທລະ​ສັບ​ ຫນ້າທີ່ເຂົາໄປຮັບຊົມ ເວລາທີ່ໃຊ້ໃນຫນ້າເວັບ ຫຼື ໃນແອັບ ແລະ ໂພສທີ່ຖືກຄລິກ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">&ldquo;</span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ຄິດຮອດ</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">&rdquo; </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ອາດຈະໃຊ້ຂໍ້ມູນນີ້ສໍາລັບການວິເຄາະ ແລະ ການຕິດຕາມຂໍ້ມູນ ກໍານົດຄວາມນິຍົມຂອງເນື້ອຫາບາງສ່ວນ ຈັດສົ່ງເນື້ອຫາທີ່ກົງກັບຄວາມສົນໃຈຂອງທ່ານໃນ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">&ldquo;</span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ຄິດຮອດ</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">&rdquo;</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;"> </span><span lang="EN-US"><br></span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; color: #202124; background: #F8F9FA; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ແລະ ເຮັດຄວາມເຂົ້າໃຈກິດຈະກໍາອອນໄລນ໌ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ດີຂຶ້ນ.</span></p>
