<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 72.0pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo11;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ໂພສທີ່ສົ່ງເສີມການແຮັກ ຫຼື </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">crack </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ໃນທຸກຮູບແບບ. ເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງຊອບແວ</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">, </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ເຊີບເວີ ຫຼືເວັບໄຊທ໌ໂດຍບໍ່ໄດ້ຮັບອະນຸຍາດ</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">;</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 20.4pt; mso-add-space: auto;"><strong><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">6.14 ເນື້ອຫາ ແລະຫນ້າເວັບທີ່ສະເໝີຄ່າຕອບແທນ</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 72.0pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo11;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ໂພສທີ່ສະເໝີຄ່າຕອບແທນ ຫຼືສິ່ງໃດກໍ່ຕາມທີ່ມີຄຸນຄ່າເປັນແຮງຈູງໃຈໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຄລິກໃສ່ການຕອບ</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">, </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ໄປຢ້ຽມຢາມເວັບໄຊທ໌</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">, </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ອ່ານອີເມວ</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">, </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ຫຼືດໍາເນີນການອື່ນ. ໃນການແລກປ່ຽນສໍາລັບບາງສິ່ງບາງຢ່າງໃນການກັບຄືນ</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 20.4pt; mso-add-space: auto;"><strong><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">6.15 ເນື້ອຫາທີ່ສືມວນຊົນເຂົ້າໃຈຜິດ</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 72.0pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo11;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ໂພສເນື້ອຫາ ແລະຮູບພາບທີ່ສືມວນຊົນເຂົ້າໃຈຜິດ ໃຫ້ຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ ການຮຽກຮ້ອງໂດຍບໍ່ມີຫຼັກຖານພຽງພໍ ແລະໜ້າເຊື່ອຖື ດ້ວຍເຈດຕະນາຫຼອກລວງ</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">, </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ບິດເບືອນ ຫຼືປິດບັງຂໍ້ມູນ ຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບຜະລິດຕະພັນແລະການບໍລິການ</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 20.4pt; mso-add-space: auto;"><strong><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">6.16ເນື້ອຫາຮຸນແຮງ</span></strong></p>
