<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 20.4pt; mso-add-space: auto;"><strong><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">6.18 ເນື້ອຫາທີ່ສົ່ງເສີມການສໍ້ໂກງ</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 56.4pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo17;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ໂພສທີ່ສະຫນັບສະຫນູນກິດຈະກໍາການສໍ້ໂກງ</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">, </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ການສໍ້ໂກງ</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">, </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ການປອມແປງເອກະສານ. ຫຼືໃຫ້ບໍລິການເອກະສານ ບົດຄວາມການສຶກສາ ຫຼືເອກະສານທາງການ</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT';">, </span><span lang="LAO" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Phetsarath OT'; mso-bidi-language: LAO;">ລວມທັງການບໍລິການສໍາລັບການສອບເສັງ</span></p>
